Posts.Title: How much do I have left?
Posts.Body: I have this weird pain in my heart every morning after waking up. My morning routine includes coffee, eggs, bacon, and a key of coke. I have increased the dosage of coke over the years as the effects were diminishing. But since the effects are not there, the consequences shouldn't be either, right?
